{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/feather.png?t=1726586168\" /><br><br>Elmin is a unique first person exploration game that seamlessly blends platforming and flying in a journey through the ruins of a long gone civilization. As the rider, you were chosen to fly on the back of a giant bird that materializes as soon as you touch a wind gust.<br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/DroptoFlight-frame.gif?t=1726586168\" /><br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/feather.png?t=1726586168\" /><br><br>Discover a meticulously designed interconnected archipelago of islands seemingly frozen in time. Explore sunken ruins and harness an ancient technology to control the elements and unlock wind routes to fly from island to island. <br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/ActivatingWinds-frame.gif?t=1726586168\" /><br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/feather.png?t=1726586168\" /><br><br>Meet the mysterious Elmin, the giant bird and guardian of the islands. What is the connection between him, the people who built those strange structures and those who brought you here in the first place ? Why did Elmin choose you as his rider ? Can you help him bring back the winds and lift the curse that plagues this forgotten land ? Is there a way out of the archipelago ?<br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/StickTheLanding-frame.gif?t=1726586168\" /><br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/fea